        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use this method to restore the state of a GIC. You can only restore a GICâ€™s state after creating a GIC device and vCPUs and before the vCPUs are running. Restore the rest of the virtual machine including GIC CPU registers with values that are compatible with the ",
              "type": "text"
            },
